{"tid":749551,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"今日個00後話唔肯ot 要計足返鐘錢比佢 真係勁無奈","createTime":"2018-07-20T06:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T20:47:15.000Z","uid":1734,"like":19,"dislike":211,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"345691af11a2b27b7014d05107f14894ef7ca9af","tid":749551,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"因為呢排公司接左大客 所以請左好多00後新人返黎幫手 勁低價9000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n咁諗住叫佢地mark下 notes 同影下野都幾好 咁呢幾晚都要ot 但老細講明班00後唔會補水 最多叫盒飯比佢地 咁其實做得office  我諗佢地都預左ot 同埋未必補錢嫁啦   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 00後 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  喂 今晚你要留低幫手開會時做文書 可能留到12點幾咁上下 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下 ... 我約左人食飯  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔得呀公司接左大job 一定要人幫手 簽約個時講左嫁啦 今晚老細會叫外賣 請埋大家 想食咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁補水補返幾多錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  下 點會有補水 d野做唔曬 就要留低做完佢啦 自己責任黎  而且你地短期合約係無ot補水 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁我唔ot啦.... <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  得 咁今個月唔洗出糧比你啦 之後屌到佢仆街 （屌左半個鐘）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後眼濕濕咁硬食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  傻鳩00後 出得社會預左嫁啦 少少野都同公司計足"},{"pid":"3948d3ada457150c2bcfa27389513eb642b72b04","tid":749551,"uid":105614,"like":101,"dislike":3,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出完呢啲膠post未<br />\n邊有咁多00後俾你屌"},{"pid":"5ae66ec2f08043b46f05d16c698381d9791efc2c","tid":749551,"uid":63432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:34:19.000Z","msg":"傻豬10後？"},{"pid":"24c0b653b9546234b829d3cf406a41dc01286f08","tid":749551,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3948d3ada457150c2bcfa27389513eb642b72b04","tid":749551,"uid":105614,"like":101,"dislike":3,"score":98,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出完呢啲膠post未<br />\n邊有咁多00後俾你屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:34:36.000Z","msg":"間公司每日運作 每日00後都有野比人屌"},{"pid":"701f0c33c0671b1682a0d95f3ff2d248cf453128","tid":749551,"uid":53798,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"唔出糧？你有權咩"},{"pid":"5f3f67d7b6439a83fca6e05fc71d36d98005626a","tid":749551,"uid":1734,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"701f0c33c0671b1682a0d95f3ff2d248cf453128","tid":749551,"uid":53798,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:35:49.000Z","msg":"唔出糧？你有權咩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"合約講到明嫁啦 佢毀約要賠錢Tim"},{"pid":"177e3cd01e16efd8ba830a4181c6839d7d233bcc","tid":749551,"uid":85564,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T06:38:16.000Z","msg":"你自己做錯野仲可以咁大聲屌返人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n係人都有權唔OT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除非你當人係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a4ac50d1733a124d31803648603d68da731346","tid":749551,"uid":53170,"like":9